blocks.text: Now, in the year 2038, we have mastered the large crises. It was a close call, yet, we just about made it. After the total financial melt-down in the year 2022, the world came to its senses. We live in radical democracy and radical bureaucracy, in a society, that knows neither hero nor villain. In a series of films, the German Pavillon shows how we arrived at this era of New Serenity.
